@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend as Frontend
participant Backend as Backend
database DB

User -> Frontend: Inserisce email e password
Frontend -> Backend: POST /Backend/v1/auth/login
Backend -> DB: Cercare utente per email
DB --> Backend: Record utente
Backend -> Backend: Verifica password
Backend -> Backend: Genera JWT
Backend --> Frontend: 200 OK { token, user }
Frontend -> Frontend: Salva token nel localStorage
@enduml